data.description: Welcome home! This delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence offers both comfort and convenience, all without the confines of an HOA, ensuring flexibility and freedom for homeowners. Nature enthusiasts will rejoice at the proximity to the renowned Fort Harrison State Park, a haven for outdoor activities. Whether you're an avid hiker, fisherman, or nature lover, this park has it all! For golf enthusiasts, the iconic The Fort Golf Resort awaits your visit, brilliantly redesigned by the legendary Pete Dye, offering a unique and challenging experience for players of all levels. Convenience is key, and this home truly delivers. Indulge in the array of amenities just a stone's throw away-savor delectable dishes at nearby restaurants, sample local brews at charming breweries, and explore an abundance of shopping options to suit every need. Additionally, the allure of Geist Reservoir is within close reach, providing a picturesque backdrop for relaxation or water-based activities. Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity to reside in a prime location that seamlessly blends natural beauty, recreational opportunities, and urban conveniences. Your perfect Indianapolis lifestyle awaits! Seller will provide a FREE 1-year HOME WARRANTY with an acceptable offer.
